channel.title: I am a strange,strange little man
channel.description:
I was playing Runescape,and i had a sudden urge to just give EVERYTHING away-so I did.
Has anyone else had this urge or do I belong in an assylum,because I had over 100m in items,and 23m cash... :cool:
I just gave it away.
